{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/5dc7d58294f1ea0017c2d418/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Rajitha's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"21d12bb0-b5a5-5ced-b120-d57c9abfa21d","excerpt":"Hi everyone, In this tutorial, weâ€™re going to build a telegram bot ,and send messages to a group with a simple HTTP request. to get start lets create a newâ€¦","html":"<h2>Hi everyone,</h2>\n<hr>\n<span style=\"font-size:1.28rem;\">\n<p>In this tutorial, weâ€™re going to build a telegram bot ,and send messages to a group with a simple HTTP request.</p>\n<p>to get start lets create a new telegram bot with, itâ€™s own API Botfather.\n</span></p>\n<h4>One Bot To Rule Them All</h4>\n<span style=\"font-size:1.28rem;\">\nso go to telegram app on your phone, or log in with [telegram web](https://web.telegram.im/#/login)\n<p>and then search for bot father.\ncreate a new bot <code class=\"language-text\">/newbot</code>\n</span></p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/d556ab859866f1cb65f04ebf9d31baff/15ec7/f61uzk32yd17rjoo8lc8.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 44.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/d556ab859866f1cb65f04ebf9d31baff/1c72d/f61uzk32yd17rjoo8lc8.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/d556ab859866f1cb65f04ebf9d31baff/a80bd/f61uzk32yd17rjoo8lc8.jpg 148w,\n/static/d556ab859866f1cb65f04ebf9d31baff/1c91a/f61uzk32yd17rjoo8lc8.jpg 295w,\n/static/d556ab859866f1cb65f04ebf9d31baff/1c72d/f61uzk32yd17rjoo8lc8.jpg 590w,\n/static/d556ab859866f1cb65f04ebf9d31baff/15ec7/f61uzk32yd17rjoo8lc8.jpg 690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<hr>\n<span style=\"font-size:1.28rem;\">\nnow follow along with instructions.\n<p>type a name for your bot\nI had a hard time finding a username ðŸ˜†\n</span></p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bec9492659b2ab1d5c1a8cbcc2c81771/eabd5/8muki02hmur8c1emb3xx.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 137.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/bec9492659b2ab1d5c1a8cbcc2c81771/1c72d/8muki02hmur8c1emb3xx.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/bec9492659b2ab1d5c1a8cbcc2c81771/a80bd/8muki02hmur8c1emb3xx.jpg 148w,\n/static/bec9492659b2ab1d5c1a8cbcc2c81771/1c91a/8muki02hmur8c1emb3xx.jpg 295w,\n/static/bec9492659b2ab1d5c1a8cbcc2c81771/1c72d/8muki02hmur8c1emb3xx.jpg 590w,\n/static/bec9492659b2ab1d5c1a8cbcc2c81771/eabd5/8muki02hmur8c1emb3xx.jpg 711w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<hr>\n<span style=\"font-size:1.28rem;\">\nnow you'll get a token to authenticate with your bot.\n</span>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/b2c6bf0ad7ab477ea379e78926569151/eafa3/q0uwbdndewa1wy5gamea.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 108.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/b2c6bf0ad7ab477ea379e78926569151/1c72d/q0uwbdndewa1wy5gamea.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/b2c6bf0ad7ab477ea379e78926569151/a80bd/q0uwbdndewa1wy5gamea.jpg 148w,\n/static/b2c6bf0ad7ab477ea379e78926569151/1c91a/q0uwbdndewa1wy5gamea.jpg 295w,\n/static/b2c6bf0ad7ab477ea379e78926569151/1c72d/q0uwbdndewa1wy5gamea.jpg 590w,\n/static/b2c6bf0ad7ab477ea379e78926569151/eafa3/q0uwbdndewa1wy5gamea.jpg 702w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<hr>\n<span style=\"font-size:1.8rem;color:red\">\n keep the access token securely. Anyone with access token can manipulate your bot\n</span>\n<span style=\"font-size:1.28rem;\">\n<p>alright, now we have the access token. The next question is how to send messages with the bot.\n</span></p>\n<hr>\n<h4>we will create a group with our bot. And then our bot will massage to that group</h4>\n<span style=\"font-size:1.28rem;\">\nit's simple as thatðŸ˜Ž\n<p>now letâ€™s create a new group in telegram and add the bot to that group.</p>\n<p>search with the username of your bot\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/89cfc818388e0edbb5857cddde14b656/721dc/jnfzasnmwb9r5klwcrdr.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 85.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/89cfc818388e0edbb5857cddde14b656/1c72d/jnfzasnmwb9r5klwcrdr.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/89cfc818388e0edbb5857cddde14b656/a80bd/jnfzasnmwb9r5klwcrdr.jpg 148w,\n/static/89cfc818388e0edbb5857cddde14b656/1c91a/jnfzasnmwb9r5klwcrdr.jpg 295w,\n/static/89cfc818388e0edbb5857cddde14b656/1c72d/jnfzasnmwb9r5klwcrdr.jpg 590w,\n/static/89cfc818388e0edbb5857cddde14b656/721dc/jnfzasnmwb9r5klwcrdr.jpg 697w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>add our bot to the group\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/8c505fa4ebed2afe670a6872c057aaef/80e3c/tecbrgdanamugyhi2ber.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 177.7027027027027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/8c505fa4ebed2afe670a6872c057aaef/1c72d/tecbrgdanamugyhi2ber.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/8c505fa4ebed2afe670a6872c057aaef/a80bd/tecbrgdanamugyhi2ber.jpg 148w,\n/static/8c505fa4ebed2afe670a6872c057aaef/1c91a/tecbrgdanamugyhi2ber.jpg 295w,\n/static/8c505fa4ebed2afe670a6872c057aaef/1c72d/tecbrgdanamugyhi2ber.jpg 590w,\n/static/8c505fa4ebed2afe670a6872c057aaef/80e3c/tecbrgdanamugyhi2ber.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>after adding give admin permission to our bot, to give access to the bot to send messages to the group (not all the permissions are necessary but I will give because this is a demo group and nothing harmful will happen ).</p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/8a0cd8023701ecd80af0df12648536ec/80e3c/f8n3zcaodh3fh7xyrxq6.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 177.7027027027027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/8a0cd8023701ecd80af0df12648536ec/1c72d/f8n3zcaodh3fh7xyrxq6.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/8a0cd8023701ecd80af0df12648536ec/a80bd/f8n3zcaodh3fh7xyrxq6.jpg 148w,\n/static/8a0cd8023701ecd80af0df12648536ec/1c91a/f8n3zcaodh3fh7xyrxq6.jpg 295w,\n/static/8a0cd8023701ecd80af0df12648536ec/1c72d/f8n3zcaodh3fh7xyrxq6.jpg 590w,\n/static/8a0cd8023701ecd80af0df12648536ec/80e3c/f8n3zcaodh3fh7xyrxq6.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>now everything is set in this end.</p>\n<p>The next thing we need is to get our group chat id to send messages to the group.</p>\n<p>to get it we need to interact with the telegram API.</p>\n<p>i hope yall have postmanðŸ“¬ ready. if not you can download <a href=\"https://www.getpostman.com/\">postman</a> , since it is a useful tool in web dev.\nor alternatively, you can use <a href=\"https://postwoman.io/\">postwoman</a> which is a great way to build requests online.</p>\n<p>before we sending requests, make sure to send some messages to our newly created group.</p>\n<p>after that letâ€™s fire up postman</p>\n<p>send a <code class=\"language-text\">POST</code> request to the following telegram API endpoint.</p>\n<p>replace <token> with your access token we previously got from bot father</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">https://api.telegram.org/bot&lt;token&gt;/getUpdates</code></p>\n<p>and Send.</p>\n<p>if you get something like this, try few more times. I donâ€™t know the exact cause, but it sometimes returns empty arrays.(make sure you have some messages in the group)</p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/902ab/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 30.405405405405407%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/1c72d/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/a80bd/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg 148w,\n/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/1c91a/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg 295w,\n/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/1c72d/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg 590w,\n/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/a8a14/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg 885w,\n/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/fbd2c/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg 1180w,\n/static/339b338489a6b0b04cc31103468cc6f4/902ab/ybfbvfi933tbguv2zmjg.jpg 1204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<hr>\n<p>hopefully, youâ€™ll receive something similar to this.</p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/00d7d/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 52.70270270270271%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/1c72d/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/a80bd/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg 148w,\n/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/1c91a/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg 295w,\n/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/1c72d/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg 590w,\n/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/a8a14/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg 885w,\n/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/fbd2c/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg 1180w,\n/static/f13e48331f42bc6fabf037127a978dc9/00d7d/ss5vjl1rb21xfp6lzuiz.jpg 1218w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<hr>\n<p>from here what we want is the chat id that starts with <code class=\"language-text\">-</code></p>\n<p>this is the group chat id of our group.</p>\n<p>after that, the only thing left is to send messages.</p>\n<p>so to send messages to our group.</p>\n<p>use the following API endpoint</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">https://api.telegram.org/bot&lt;token&gt;/sendMessage?chat_id=&lt;group chat id &gt;&amp;text=&lt;our text&gt;</code></p>\n<p>keep in mind that text should be URL Encoding String</p>\n<p>ex - Hello%20World (spaces is replaced with %20)</p>\n<p>checkout <a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/ref_urlencode.asp\">w3school</a> for more info</p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/1839c/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 57.432432432432435%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/1c72d/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/a80bd/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg 148w,\n/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/1c91a/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg 295w,\n/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/1c72d/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg 590w,\n/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/a8a14/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg 885w,\n/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/fbd2c/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg 1180w,\n/static/2979e2b2c3a0fb3ce327da41fada9e91/1839c/e1n9y2kf7xy53jxsxmlj.jpg 1196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<hr>\n<p>and <code class=\"language-text\">wubba lubba dub dub</code> your message is sent</p>\n<hr>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bfe635ded3a1558995b9458e8dadaae9/80e3c/v3c57ifyl2npx5g3m63m.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 177.7027027027027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"create new bot\" title=\"create new bot\" src=\"/static/bfe635ded3a1558995b9458e8dadaae9/1c72d/v3c57ifyl2npx5g3m63m.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/bfe635ded3a1558995b9458e8dadaae9/a80bd/v3c57ifyl2npx5g3m63m.jpg 148w,\n/static/bfe635ded3a1558995b9458e8dadaae9/1c91a/v3c57ifyl2npx5g3m63m.jpg 295w,\n/static/bfe635ded3a1558995b9458e8dadaae9/1c72d/v3c57ifyl2npx5g3m63m.jpg 590w,\n/static/bfe635ded3a1558995b9458e8dadaae9/80e3c/v3c57ifyl2npx5g3m63m.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<hr>\n</span>\n<h4>This is a great way to monitor and notify your apps state. I use this for the backend of my web apps to report errors. you can also use it with frontends, CLI applications regardless of the language. you can use this creatively to do many things because this needs no 3rd party libraries or dependencies, just a simple HTTP request will do the work.</h4>\n<hr>\n<h3>Thanks for following along with me ðŸ™Œ</h3>\n<h2>what are your plans ? ðŸ’­</h2>\n<h2>share them in the comments section.</h2>\n<h2>Iâ€™d love to hear your feedback!</h2>\n<h3>originaly posted on <a href=\"https://dev.to/rizkyrajitha/get-notifications-with-telegram-bot-537l\">Dev.to</a></h3>","frontmatter":{"id":"5dc7d58294f1ea0017c2d418","title":"Sending messages with Telegram bot","date":"November 10, 2019","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/5dc7d58294f1ea0017c2d418/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/5dc7ac019b6e62001738620e/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"First official post"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/5dc8453252d6640017e5e22a/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Heroku Gotchas, Before you deploy"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}